    {
      "id": "3M76hMRz9ZWgOLL1cOYD6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -358.66652425130155,
      "y": 2851.278010050456,
      "width": 768.33984375,
      "height": 575,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "av",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1699918717,
      "version": 509,
      "versionNonce": 1280569815,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783519612183,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "***************************** Binary Search *****************************\n\n1) Array is sorted and value can be either on left or right side.\n2) Array is not sorted but need to find answer \n   and answer is monotonic increase or decrease.\n3) Max(min of value) or Min(max of vlaue)\n\n| If Question Says               | Pattern                    |\n| ----------------------------       | -------------------------- |\n| Find element in sorted array | Classic Binary Search      |\n| First/Last occurrence         | Boundary Binary Search     |\n| Search insert position         | Lower Bound                |\n| Find smallest X                 | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Find largest X                  | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Minimum speed                  | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Minimum capacity               | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Maximum distance              | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Rotated sorted array        | Rotated Binary Search      |\n| Peak/Mountain                 | Peak Binary Search         |\n| Median of two arrays         | Partition Binary Search    |\n| Square root                     | Binary Search on Value     |\n| Floating answer                | Binary Search on Precision |\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "***************************** Binary Search *****************************\n\n1) Array is sorted and value can be either on left or right side.\n2) Array is not sorted but need to find answer \n   and answer is monotonic increase or decrease.\n3) Max(min of value) or Min(max of vlaue)\n\n| If Question Says               | Pattern                    |\n| ----------------------------       | -------------------------- |\n| Find element in sorted array | Classic Binary Search      |\n| First/Last occurrence         | Boundary Binary Search     |\n| Search insert position         | Lower Bound                |\n| Find smallest X                 | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Find largest X                  | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Minimum speed                  | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Minimum capacity               | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Maximum distance              | Binary Search on Answer    |\n| Rotated sorted array        | Rotated Binary Search      |\n| Peak/Mountain                 | Peak Binary Search         |\n| Median of two arrays         | Partition Binary Search    |\n| Square root                     | Binary Search on Value     |\n| Floating answer                | Binary Search on Precision |\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "JMAqWksI3s7cHgNRvpiWg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -361.66652425130155,
      "y": 3448.778010050456,
      "width": 421.7895202636719,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1679338899,
      "version": 47,
      "versionNonce": 1216215833,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783519612183,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Is array sorted?\n│\n├── Yes\n│      │\n│      ├── Exact element?\n│      │       → Exact Search\n│      │\n│      ├── First/Last occurrence?\n│      │       → Lower/Upper Bound\n│      │\n│      └── Rotated?\n│              → Rotated Binary Search\n│\n└── No\n       │\n       ├── Can answer space be ordered?\n       │\n       ├── Does check(mid) produce\n       │   F F F T T T\n       │\n       └── Yes  → Binary Search on Answer",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Is array sorted?\n│\n├── Yes\n│      │\n│      ├── Exact element?\n│      │       → Exact Search\n│      │\n│      ├── First/Last occurrence?\n│      │       → Lower/Upper Bound\n│      │\n│      └── Rotated?\n│              → Rotated Binary Search\n│\n└── No\n       │\n       ├── Can answer space be ordered?\n       │\n       ├── Does check(mid) produce\n       │   F F F T T T\n       │\n       └── Yes  → Binary Search on Answer",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
